ompetition is also held at the regional and national levels.\", \"from\": 1761, \"to\": 1855, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the global event\", \"from\": 1772, \"to\": 1788}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 1790, \"to\": 1805}, {\"ngram\": \"the regional and national levels\", \"from\": 1822, \"to\": 1854}]}, {\"sentence\": \"InSeptember, 35 young people from ITE, polytechnics and SBS Transit will represent Singapore in 30 skill areas at the 47th WorldSkills competition in Lyon, France, to be held from Sept 10 to 15.\", \"from\": 1857, \"to\": 2051, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1891, \"end\": 1894, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Institute_of_Technical_Education\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.072543384069282e-25, \"text\": \"ITE\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Institute_of_Technical_Education\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Institute_of_Technical_Education\"}, {\"begin\": 1940, \"end\": 1949, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1372297225108906e-18, \"text\": \"Singapore\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\"}, {\"begin\": 2007, \"end\": 2011, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyon\", \"score\": 0.9999995964445493, \"rank\": 4.0353823447169806e-07, \"text\": \"Lyon\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyon\"}, {\"begin\": 2013, \"end\": 2019, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.999723732036078, \"rank\": 0.0002248906649139265, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"35 young people\", \"from\": 1870, \"to\": 1885}, {\"ngram\": \"polytechnics\", \"from