9}, {\"ngram\": \"make-up expertise\", \"from\": 2714, \"to\": 2731}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said the challenge will lie in knowing the types of products she has to use, as she may not be familiar with some of them.\", \"from\": 2734, \"to\": 2860, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the challenge\", \"from\": 2743, \"to\": 2756}, {\"ngram\": \"the types\", \"from\": 2777, \"to\": 2786}, {\"ngram\": \"products\", \"from\": 2790, \"to\": 2798}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I might not know how a product works, because different products work differently.\", \"from\": 2862, \"to\": 2945, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a product\", \"from\": 2884, \"to\": 2893}, {\"ngram\": \"different products\", \"from\": 2909, \"to\": 2927}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nonetheless, I have the general knowledge and I have practised, so I will do my best,\\\" said Ms Huang, who since 2023 has been spending most of her free time before and after school preparing for the competition.\", \"from\": 2946, \"to\": 3157, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the general knowledge\", \"from\": 2966, \"to\": 2987}, {\"ngram\": \"Ms Huang\", \"from\": 3038, \"to\": 3046}, {\"ngram\": \"her free time\", \"from\": 3089, \"to\": 3102}, {\"ngram\": \"school\", \"from\": 3120, \"to\": 3126}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 3141, \"to\": 3156}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ms Christine Huang (left) and her mentor for the upcoming WorldSkills competition, Ms Shuner Villanueva Leong.\", \"from\": 3159, \"to\": 3269, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3162, \"end\": 3171, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christine_Blair\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.536261942992123e-19, \"text\": \"Christine\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christine_Blair\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christine_Blair\"}, {\"begin\": 3252, \"end\": 3262, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlie_Villanueva\", \"score\": 0.4519701